{"id":263740,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/global-voices-希腊：请愿要求禁止歧视委员会撤职金色黎明/","date":"2012-11-18T11:45:11Z","modified":"2012-11-18T11:45:11Z","title":"Global Voices | 希腊：请愿要求禁止歧视委员会撤职金色黎明党议员","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>一直以来，<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%87%91%E8%89%B2%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E5%85%9A\">金色黎明党</a>以其仇外与反闪语族的露骨言论而恶名昭彰。该党也是攻击犹太人与外国人的罪魁祸首。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>欧盟犹太学生组织（European Union of Jewish Students）发起<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.eujs.org/news/article/133\">请愿</a>， 强烈要求欧洲理事会议会平等与禁止歧视委员会（Committee on Equality and Non-Discrimination of the Parliamentary Assembly of the Council of Europe）解除该会金色黎明党国会议员<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://assembly.coe.int/ASP/AssemblyList/AL_MemberDetails.asp?MemberID=6978\">Eleni Zaroulia</a>的职务。Zaroulia最近在希腊国会发言时，<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6Y09xr846cg\">以“次等人”来谈论外来移民</a>希腊文。希腊犹太社群中央委员会（Central Board of Jewish Communities in Greece）也发表一封<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.kis.gr/en/index.php?option=com_content&#038;view=article&#038;id=451:greek-jewry-protests-for-golden-dawn-membership-to-non-discrimination-committee-of-the-coe&#038;catid=49:2009-05-11-09-28-23\">信函</a>，要求撤职Zaroulia。</p>\n<div>校对：Portnoy</div>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/asteris-masouras/\" title=\"文章导读 Asteris Masouras\">Asteris Masouras</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/ameli/\" title=\"文章导读 Ameli\">Ameli</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/10/18/greece-petition-to-remove-golden-dawn-mp-from-non-discrimination-committee/\" title=\"阅读原文  en\">阅读原文  en</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2012/11/18/11767/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E5%B8%8C%E8%85